---
// Vision Section - Bigger Picture & Roadmap
---

<section class="section-container bg-deep-space/50" id="vision">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-animate">
      <div class="ascii-divider text-center mb-6">
        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-mono font-bold text-solana-green mb-4">
        THE VISION: A World Where Anyone Can Build on Solana
      </h2>
      <div class="ascii-divider text-center mt-6">
        ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Today vs Tomorrow -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16">
      <!-- Today -->
      <div class="scroll-animate delay-200">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-mono text-pink-error mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">📛</span> Today, blockchain development is gated by:
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-slate-secondary">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-pink-error">├─</span>
            <span>Specialized knowledge (Rust, cryptography, Solana runtime)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-pink-error">├─</span>
            <span>Time-intensive setup (weeks of toolchain configuration)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-pink-error">├─</span>
            <span>Capital barriers (expensive developer talent)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-pink-error">└─</span>
            <span>Fear of mistakes (lost funds, security holes)</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Tomorrow -->
      <div class="scroll-animate delay-300">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-mono text-solana-green mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-2xl">✨</span> Tomorrow, with SolCoder:
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 font-mono text-slate-secondary">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-solana-green">├─</span>
            <span>Natural language is the only requirement</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-solana-green">├─</span>
            <span>AI agents handle scaffolding, testing, deployment</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-solana-green">├─</span>
            <span>Secure wallet autonomy with spend policies</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-solana-green">├─</span>
            <span>Built-in Solana expertise (no Googling required)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-solana-green">└─</span>
            <span>Open-source, community-driven, unstoppable</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vision Statement -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16 scroll-animate delay-400">
      <div class="ascii-divider mb-8">─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</div>
      <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-mono text-slate-primary mb-4">
        We're building more than a tool.
      </p>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-solana-green mb-6">
        We're building the operating system for the next
        <br />
        <span class="gradient-text font-bold">million Solana developers.</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-secondary max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        From solo hackers in Nairobi to serial founders in SF,
        <br />
        from 16-year-old prodigies to career-switching nurses—
      </p>
      <p class="text-2xl font-mono text-solana-green mt-6">
        If you can describe your idea, you can build it.
      </p>
      <div class="ascii-divider mt-8">─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Roadmap Timeline -->
    <div class="scroll-animate delay-500">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-mono text-center text-solana-green mb-8">
        🗺️ Roadmap: Building the Future
      </h3>

      <div class="space-y-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Phase 1 -->
        <div class="feature-card border-solana-green">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-mono text-solana-purple flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>🟣</span> PHASE 1: HACKATHON MVP
            </h4>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-mono px-3 py-1 bg-solana-green/20 text-solana-green rounded-full"
              >COMPLETE</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="w-full bg-deep-space border border-solana-green/30 rounded-full h-3">
              <div class="h-full bg-solana-green rounded-full" style="width: 100%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-secondary font-mono">
            └─ CLI agent with wallet + deploy + knowledge base
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 2 -->
        <div class="feature-card border-cyan-info">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-mono text-solana-green flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>🟢</span> PHASE 2: DEPIN INFERENCE
            </h4>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-mono px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-info/20 text-cyan-info rounded-full"
              >Q1 2025</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="w-full bg-deep-space border border-cyan-info/30 rounded-full h-3">
              <div class="h-full bg-cyan-info rounded-full animate-progress" style="--progress: 65%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-secondary font-mono">
            └─ Decentralized LLM calls, Solana-settled pricing
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 3 -->
        <div class="feature-card border-solana-purple">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-mono text-solana-purple flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>🟣</span> PHASE 3: SCR TOKEN
            </h4>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-mono px-3 py-1 bg-solana-purple/20 text-solana-purple rounded-full"
              >Q2 2025</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="w-full bg-deep-space border border-solana-purple/30 rounded-full h-3">
              <div class="h-full bg-solana-purple rounded-full" style="width: 30%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-secondary font-mono">
            └─ Native token for inference, staking, governance
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Phase 4 -->
        <div class="feature-card border-amber-warn">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <h4 class="text-lg font-mono text-solana-green flex items-center gap-2">
              <span>🟢</span> PHASE 4: AGENT NETWORK
            </h4>
            <span
              class="text-xs font-mono px-3 py-1 bg-amber-warn/20 text-amber-warn rounded-full"
              >Q3 2025+</span
            >
          </div>
          <div class="mb-3">
            <div class="w-full bg-deep-space border border-amber-warn/30 rounded-full h-3">
              <div class="h-full bg-amber-warn rounded-full" style="width: 10%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-secondary font-mono space-y-1">
            <p>└─ Autonomous agents improving Solana ecosystem</p>
            <p class="ml-4">└─ On-chain reputation, cryptographic contributions</p>
            <p class="ml-4">└─ Agents audit code, submit PRs, earn rewards</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- End Goal -->
        <div class="text-center mt-8 p-6 border-2 border-gradient-hero rounded-lg bg-gradient-hero/5">
          <p class="text-xl font-mono text-solana-green flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <span>💡</span>
            <span>END GOAL: 10,000+ AI agents maintaining Solana</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
